          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd. I. Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>Pen</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>London</placeName>
                                        <date>11<hi rend="sup">th</hi> March 1853</date>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>2 Heneags Lane, Bevis<add>?</add>
                                                  Marks</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p>Revd Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">It is with deep regret that I<lb/> inform you of
                                        the demise of the <persName>Revd D.<lb/> Meldola</persName>
                                        <add>Hebrew</add> which took place rather<lb/> suddenly on
                                                  <date>Wednesday 2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi></date>
                                        Inst., he<lb/> had been indisposed for about two months<lb/>
                                        and a half with a disease of the throat &amp;<lb/> lungs,
                                        but no person, not even his medi-<lb/>-cal advisers had an
                                        idea that he was<lb/> so near his death. I can assure
                                        you<lb/> that he always had a very high opinion<lb/> of you
                                        and deservedly so. May I request<lb/> that you will be kind
                                        enough to insert<lb/> something in the “Occident”
                                        concerning<lb/> our departed friend, “Peace be with him”</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I have sent you the “Hebrew Observer.”<lb/> in
                                        which you will find an account of the<lb/> funeral.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Hoping you are well</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">I remain</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Revd. Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">yours truly</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">David Piza</persName>
                              </p>
